    <para id="id3760700">III. DT FILTERS</para>
    <para id="id3760704">A variety of DT filters can be synthesized.</para>
    <list id="id3520455" list-type="bulleted">
      <item>DT filters similar to CT filters can be synthesized, e.g., lowpass filters, highpass filters, bandpass filters, bandreject filters, notchfilters</item>
    </list>
    <list id="id8418835" list-type="bulleted">
      <item>DT filters synthesized from recursive difference equations</item>
    </list>
    <para id="id9423030">
      <m:math>
        <m:semantics>
