    <para id="id4928456">IV. CONCLUSIONS ON DT FILTERS</para>
    <list id="id4928459" list-type="bulleted">
      <item>Real poles between z = 0 and z = 1  lowpass filter.</item>
    </list>
    <list id="id6112978" list-type="bulleted">
      <item>Real zeros between z = −1 and z = 0  lowpass filter.</item>
    </list>
    <list id="id9801170" list-type="bulleted">
      <item>Real poles between z = −1 and z = 0  highpass filter.</item>
    </list>
    <list id="id4445142" list-type="bulleted">
      <item>Real zeros between z = 0 and z = 1  highpass filter.</item>
    </list>
    <list id="id8102518" list-type="bulleted">
      <item>Complex conjugate poles with |z| &lt;1  bandpass filter.</item>
    </list>
    <list id="id3754849" list-type="bulleted">
      <item>Complex conjugate zeros with |z| &lt;1  bandreject filter.</item>
    </list>
    <list id="id9116578" list-type="bulleted">
      <item>Complex conjugate poles 
<m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mstyle fontsize="12pt"><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">∣</m:mo><m:mi>α</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">∣</m:mo><m:msup><m:mi>e</m:mi><m:mstyle fontsize="8pt"><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>j</m:mi><m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">Ω</m:mo><m:mstyle fontsize="6pt"><m:mrow><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mstyle></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mstyle></m:msup></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mstyle><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ \lline α \lline e rSup { size 8{j %OMEGA  rSub { size 6{0} } } } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math>, have center frequencies that increase as 
<m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mstyle fontsize="12pt"><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mo stretchy="false">Ω</m:mo><m:mstyle fontsize="8pt"><m:mrow><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mstyle></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mstyle><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ %OMEGA  rSub { size 8{0} } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> increases.</item>
    </list>
    <list id="id3791585" list-type="bulleted">
      <item>Complex conjugate poles and zeros nearer the unit circle yield filters with narrower bandwidth.</item>
